{"tid":423832,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"第四起iPhone8電池鼓脹來了：機身慘不忍睹","createTime":"2017-10-04T08:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T09:29:01.000Z","uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adae295d0783ad9b4992e3b918f428de7c270930","tid":423832,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"蘋果手機iPhone 8系列開賣已來，在台灣、日本、香港先後傳出多起電池鼓脹事件。<br />\n<br />\n10月3日日在台中也傳出一起案例，據業者表示，這支iPhone 8是在待機狀態下無預警鼓脹變形，向蘋果客服聯絡後對方僅說，會反映給美國總公司工程部，這第四起了電池鼓脹事件了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1ijbh6/3r5n0002311ps3qn87qo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1ijbh6%2F3r5n0002311ps3qn87qo.jpg&h=e4bfacd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔣姓業者提到，顧客的手機有充過電，通話時會有類似電流的雜音，事發當天顧客只是把手機拿在手上，沒有使用也沒有在充電，手機也沒有發熱的現象，卻突然膨脹變形、機身爆開，讓他相當傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2noipm8/3r5n0002311qp49q3qp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2noipm8%2F3r5n0002311qp49q3qp0.jpg&h=3e221950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dec026ef4aa3ea9a27b2a2c14444cefc7bbda0f","tid":423832,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"Apple: 過左十單先同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8e4306396569fb102f544344dfb9eaaf7a3beb","tid":423832,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"iphone8 有新名未？"},{"pid":"6afc50700861e9985ad1acff71d336ad62d50d43","tid":423832,"uid":137835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iphone8 有新名未？</blockquote><br />\napple note7"},{"pid":"bdc982486d8da856ab47b91224f0b719c43d8ed2","tid":423832,"uid":22553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>i